SASMSMMSAMXSAMXSMXMMMSSMSXSSMSSSXMMXMAMMMMMAMAMXXSAMXMAXXXXSAMXSXSMMMMMMXXMSMSSMSSXMMMAMXMMSAMXXAXSMMXXMMMMASXSSMMSMSMSSSMSMMASXSMSMMMSMMMSM
